OL,6,FPremier League clubs have voted in
OL,7,Ffavour of investigating how to
OL,8,Fintroduce a spending cap, which could
OL,9,Fpass as early as June if all clubs
OL,10,Fagree.
OL,12,FBut ITV News understands Manchester
OL,13,FUnited and Manchester City voted
OL,14,Fagainst it on Monday.
