OL,3,CPremier League spending cap backed by
OL,4,Cmost clubs but will the richest agree?
OL,6,FClubs voted on Monday to progress to
OL,7,Fthe final stages of a legal and
OL,8,Feconomic analysis of anchoring ` a
OL,9,Fprinciple which would potentially
OL,10,Flimit expenditure on player wages,
OL,11,Fplus agents' fees and transfer
OL,12,Famortisation costs, by capping them as
OL,13,Fa multiple of the central Premier
OL,14,FLeague revenues going to the bottom
OL,15,Fclub.
OL,17,FThe intention of anchoring is to keep
OL,18,Fthe league competitive by preventing
OL,19,Fthe richest clubs dominating.
