OL,3,CPremier League spending cap backed by
OL,4,Cmost clubs but will the richest agree?
OL,6,FAnchoring, if approved, would be one
OL,7,Fpart of the new squad cost control
OL,8,Fmeasures which are set to replace the
OL,9,Fexisting profitability and
OL,10,Fsustainability regulations (PSR) from
OL,11,Fthe 2025-26 season.
OL,13,FClubs unanimously voted in support of
OL,14,Fsquad spending caps linked to revenue
OL,15,Fbeing a key principle within those new
OL,16,Frules at a meeting on April 11.
