OL,3,CPremier League spending cap backed by
OL,4,Cmost clubs but will the richest agree?
OL,6,FClubs playing in European competition
OL,7,Ffrom 2025-26 will need to limit squad-
OL,8,Frelated costs ` including spending on
OL,9,Ftransfer and agents' fees plus wages `
OL,10,Fto 70 per cent of revenue in order to
OL,11,Fabide by UEFA's rules.
OL,13,FIt is understood Premier League clubs
OL,14,Fare expected to be limited to 85 per
OL,15,Fcent of revenue, with points
OL,16,Fdeductions still likely to be applied
OL,17,Fwhere breaches of the ratio are
OL,18,Fserious.
