OL,3,CPremier League spending cap backed by
OL,4,Cmost clubs but will the richest agree?
OL,6,FWhile the squad cost to revenue rules
OL,7,Fwould effectively place spending
OL,8,Flimits on aspiring clubs who do not
OL,9,Fhave the same earning power as more
OL,10,Festablished clubs, anchoring ` if
OL,11,Fapproved ` would create a 'hard'
OL,12,Fceiling for the biggest and richest
OL,13,Fclubs which has no direct link to the
OL,14,Frevenue they earn.
