OL,3,CPremier League spending cap backed by
OL,4,Cmost clubs but will the richest agree?
OL,6,FRules on anchoring are now set to be
OL,7,Fdrafted, and could be voted on at the
OL,8,Fleague's annual general meeting in
OL,9,FJune. However, the PFA will need to be
OL,10,Fconvinced that the measures do not
OL,11,Fplace limits on what its members can
OL,12,Fearn.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the PFA said on
OL,15,FMonday: "We will obviously wait to see
OL,16,Ffurther details of these specific
OL,17,Fproposals, but we have always been
OL,18,Fclear that we would oppose any measure
OL,19,Fthat would place a 'hard' cap on
OL,20,Fplayer wages.
